Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1405
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 12-7-2; IC 12-10-16.5; IC 35-52-12-1.5.
Synopsis: Prescription drug assistance program for the elderly.
Establishes the prescription drug assistance program for the elderly
(program) to be administered by the division of aging. Sets forth
requirements of the program. Establishes the prescription drug
assistance program for the elderly fund. Creates a Class A
misdemeanor for fraud under the program.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Carbaugh
January 8, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Public Health.
